description:
Contents:
 - Spring Tea Party Garb: Galphin "Spring clothing inspired by Devon tea-parties."
 - Kid's Tea Party Garb: Galphin "Spring children's clothing inspired by Devon tea-parties."
 *You can buy it at any time in the game shop (Clothing Store in Castle St.) when you purchase it.
 - Hatter's Hat: Red "A custom silk hat made by a hatter. Price tag included."
 - Rabbit-Ear Hat: Red "A silk hat with fluffy rabbit ears."
 - Red Rabbit Mask "A mask modeled after a rabbit's face."
 *You can buy it at any time in the game shop (Fashion Store in Castle St.) when you purchase it.
name: Tea-party (Galphin)
